              "<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/manifest.json/permissions\">https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/manifest.json/permissions</a>",
              "Note that on Safari permission system is non-existent. This module assumes that Safari has all permissions."
            ],
